popt4jlib.neural

Class TanH01

  • java.lang.Object
    • popt4jlib.neural.BaseNNNode
      • popt4jlib.neural.TanH01
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, NNNodeIntf

    public class TanH01
extends BaseNNNode
implements NNNodeIntf
    TanH01 implements the tanh function, scaled and shifted so as to produce values in [0,1] as activation function of a node. Can only be used as hidden layer node.

    Title: popt4jlib
